r coaster you are in can be destroyed\nFeel referents Sensations\n\n-Apocalypse Shoot the Asteroids\nInteractive Roller Coaster ride at apolacalypse environment\nHere you can shoot and destroy the asteroids, with a powerful laser\nYou can ride and make a new score at each new ride.\n\n-Before Apocalypse\nHere you can enjoy a slow ride with no loops at a sunny day.\nAt this experience there is no apocalypse \n\nRoller Coaster at Immersive Apocalypse environment\nYou can ride and feel the Apocalypse environment", "short_description": "Three roller coasters with a Interactive Roller Coaster\nThree different experiences, rides:\n-Apocalypse Destruction\n-Apocalypse Shoot the Asteroids\n-Before Apocalypse\n\nRoller Coaster at Immersive Apocalypse environment\nYou can ride, play and feel the Apocalypse environment\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.netdinamica.com.br/games/rollercoastereapocalypse/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.netdinamica.com.br/games/rollercoastereapocalypse/terms.html", "publisher_name": "NetDinamica", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.netdinamica.com.br/games/rollercoastereapocalypse", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ROLLER_COASTER", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_US", "en_AU", "en_CA", "en_ZA", "en_GB"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "279651834256288"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/11162685_1710872062273266_5435937444220370944